{"tid":343570,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖][突發奇想] 點解唔可以一邊嘆冷氣一邊發電 ?","createTime":"2017-08-01T14:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T02:19:55.000Z","uid":97606,"like":178,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1bcaf497cb32c6905c79a72957b1fc6e2de80a5","tid":343570,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"眾所周知, 冷氣可以將<span style=\"color: red;\">熱空氣</span>轉換成<span style=\"color: teal;\">冷空氣</span><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">熱空氣</span>轉換成<span style=\"color: teal;\">冷空氣</span>既同時, 會失去<span style=\"color: orange;\">熱能</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/223243_a852468ec27aca9ff0ff85467aadf8d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F223243_a852468ec27aca9ff0ff85467aadf8d9.png&h=881983d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果可以設計一部好似上面幅圖既冷氣, 係咪可以實現到一邊嘆冷氣一邊發電既願望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求連登物理學家入黎解答<br />\n<br />\n利申: 知道冷氣機基本運作原理, 純粹學術交流下可能性"},{"pid":"20ea58fca47771454c3f27a90c5bf2143d192cdf","tid":343570,"uid":2959,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"你知得太多了"},{"pid":"bfd9d9342fcb16a7d2bdb25255f82f0c24ee6a1f","tid":343570,"uid":97126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正評俾圖"},{"pid":"099ac7609189185b4cb6e1dbcaa87f432a1004e0","tid":343570,"uid":53973,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"一早有<br />\n利申 發夢見過"},{"pid":"a89ad55a9a7e92