},{"pid":"bda83588a4843e712e27b4503c240651bb69f0a9","tid":343570,"uid":42064,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果咁講，入邊轉緊嘅風扇其實都係一種動能，可以用個電池儲返起佢，好似汽車電池咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：亂噏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再生制動就係呢個原理</blockquote><br />\n再生制動發電係動能&rarr;電，發電係要拎走d動能，即係你架車由快變慢／停。<br />\n<br />\n風扇你拎走d動能，咪即係細風左，本沒倒置。而有風亦因為你俾電摩打，即係電&rarr;動&rarr;電。<br />\n最後風細左，發電會有能量損耗，即係哂左電。"},{"pid":"9d8162b53e93c3219cff798fb04e5656cad7fcd1","tid":343570,"uid":68491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"如果咁既熱能都夠發電, 仲洗咩太陽能搞咁多野"},{"pid":"5cfeec90525204e7908721d4698af771dd6dd6e7","tid":343570,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"呢塊野可以調轉用溫差發電?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aeeq-gKX01o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Daeeq-gKX01o&d=eThoJcB1ACfYqYpccgV6HgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=1d951688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aeeq-gKX01o</a>"},{"pid":"70bba6ebf04414be9d6a7cb1ace3d68f295e3833","tid":343570,"uid":108993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"heat loss = no useful work ???<br />\n利申：9 up <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bbdd6ebd84b82e006c313fe3562653b80c139f3","tid":343570,"uid":96855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"用更多嘅電去發更少嘅電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9ec86f8688a2c5e8838c8a838b920fc489ae98","tid":343570,"uid":110125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"睇完refrigeration cycle你就明點解唔得"},{"pid":"f3d3318bba04d9eb65806a0be11151bbd9f6646f","tid":343570,"uid":74285,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:13:42.000Z","msg":"你知唔知發電原理 <br />\n幾乎全部發電機都係因為動能轉電能<br />\n例如 一般用熱能發電  都係用熱將水煮沸 用水蒸氣推動渦輪轉電<br />\n咁你冷氣機咁小熱點令水沸騰<br />\n就當你好多熱可以令水沸騰  個發電效率 一定遠低過你用製冷的電<br />\n<br />\n所以話係唔可行<br />\n大佬呀 科學家諗咁撚多年都解決唔到 <br />\n你估佢地冇諗呢個問題咩<br />\n<br />\n利申：認真左 （樓主真膠定假膠）"},{"pid":"7807395d431cbdca3fbeb19bebb81e1556f0837c","tid":343570,"uid":34771,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:16:46.000Z","msg":"睇見依個post咁多正評<br />\n就知道勁多小學雞"},{"pid":"220f5765cddb366c15389c761ab9ed6369967ddc","tid":343570,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"輸出大過輸入咪解釋左囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16203da9b3635fe6230c5c21ebb59fa3ebb60e3","tid":343570,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇見依個post咁多正評<br />\n就知道勁多小學雞</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f999579c6dad33b00269a052a506d390141b5eb","tid":343570,"uid":66951,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"Refrigeration cycle都唔曉係度9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f693018499ae49e5652a1b09bfde680c6ca668","tid":343570,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:31:20.000Z","msg":"D熱量咁少<br />\n最多咪得 30 40度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n效益低到仆街"},{"pid":"7e3d8bf570a819872d0cac406c145fe8c2ec9357","tid":343570,"uid":54390,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://3.im.guokr.com/msXqAMxW5lilrL2XaMnbwMKKzFI0Ykwl7wVQT4tzgdhNAQAAsAAAAEdJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F3.im.guokr.com%2FmsXqAMxW5lilrL2XaMnbwMKKzFI0Ykwl7wVQT4tzgdhNAQAAsAAAAEdJ.gif&h=46